# What does NOT ship to Railway. Deploys MUST use `railway up --no-gitignore`
# (plain `railway up` silently drops gitignored files — and the gitignored
# kairos/ IS the workspace). That makes this file the ONLY exclusion list,
# so secrets and junk are listed here explicitly.
node_modules
.git
logs
creatoros
deploy
dist
.env
.DS_Store
*.log

# Everything else SHIPS on purpose — the worker needs it:
#   src/ + package files + Dockerfile.worker   the code it runs
#   kairos/                                    config, skills, automations.json
#   templates/                                 skill templates
#   content-library/                           media the posting automations publish
